1
00:00:37,237 --> 00:00:39,238
Get packed. We leave tomorrow.

2
00:00:39,239 --> 00:00:41,239
The sponsor wants you
two to build some chemistry.

3
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:51,550
What?

4
00:00:51,918 --> 00:00:53,319
You'll be okay on your own?

5
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:56,423
Please, I'm not a little kid.

6
00:00:56,890 --> 00:00:59,091
Hey, it's just you and Hei Yan alone.

7
00:00:59,092 --> 00:00:59,993
Honestly...

8
00:00:59,994 --> 00:01:01,314
Why can't the manager come along?

9
00:01:02,328 --> 00:01:03,296
What's there to worry about?

10
00:01:03,297 --> 00:01:04,931
It's just two guys. What could happen?

11
00:01:05,131 --> 00:01:05,865
I'm telling you,

12
00:01:05,866 --> 00:01:08,167
they're filming everything,
so watch yourself.

13
00:01:08,168 --> 00:01:09,301
I'm worried Lin Bingchen

14
00:01:09,302 --> 00:01:10,470
might pull some dirty tricks.

15
00:01:10,870 --> 00:01:12,071
Whatever beef you two have,

16
00:01:12,072 --> 00:01:13,306
don't drag us into it.

17
00:01:14,007 --> 00:01:15,007
Bye!

18
00:01:22,615 --> 00:01:24,215
You're so heartless, it's making me cry.

19
00:01:24,818 --> 00:01:26,738
You're off to spend your
time with someone else,

20
00:01:27,187 --> 00:01:29,622
... no matter how I look at it,
that doesn't look like me.

21
00:01:30,323 --> 00:01:31,491
Oh my god.

22
00:01:39,165 --> 00:01:40,165
Oh, right.

23
00:01:43,336 --> 00:01:46,706
Don't forget to give it back to him.

24
00:02:05,291 --> 00:02:06,493
We're going to be late!

25
00:02:17,637 --> 00:02:20,039
Just three more minutes.

26
00:02:23,843 --> 00:02:26,478
Three minutes is plenty.

27
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:29,015
You sleep, and I'll kiss you.
